dblAuth: Authentication code for dbl voting webhook
debug: true/false | true - prevents bot from sending guild count to dbl.org, false - sends data
encryptionAuth: Authentication for encrpyting users inventories and decoding encyptions using AES
logChannel: ID of channel to send logs to ie. trade logs, kill logs, cooldown dodgers.
modChannel: ID of channel where moderators can use mod-only commands. Good for allowing admins to monitor moderators.
